{
  "stem": "1692.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 445.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And my mother really felt very bad and guilty that all her friends and relatives didn't have any children anymore.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And she still had her two daughters.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So we used to stay in the house a lot.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But then a ghetto was formed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And everybody would go to work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And if there wasn't much work, and if you didn't work, you didn't get any bread.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I didn't have a job.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my mother was terribly afraid they'll take me away.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So one day, I went to the Judenrat.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a-- Judenrat's a council of elders that was elected to run the ghetto-- to see if there was any work available.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I saw some people signing up to go pick hops, 12 kilometers from the city.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So a few of my friends and I signed up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I worked there from sunrise to sundown, eating only potato soup.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that's when I got very sick with dysentery-- so crippled with cramps-- I couldn't work.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they sent me back to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And just because of that, I survived.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because when I came home, and I was very sick-- so I don't know-- or my mother got a doctor.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I don't know where she got some things what to feed me with.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this was about two days before orders came that we should all be at noon, at a certain place.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we knew already what this meant.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "By then, every family had a hiding place-- a hiding place that we used to call malina.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Malina means a raspberry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But that was our code.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The ghetto was created after the second [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had three [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The first, they killed the old and the sick.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The second one, they killed all the young people.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
